#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.signbit.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.signbit"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.signbit.signbit:1 of
msgid "Returns element-wise True where signbit is set (less than zero)."
msgstr "返回逐元素的布尔值，当符号位被设置时（即小于零）为 True。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.signbit.signbit of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.signbit.signbit:3 of
msgid "The input value(s)."
msgstr "输入值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.signbit.signbit:5 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，其形状必须可以广播到输入形状。如果未提供或"
"为 `None`，将返回一个新分配的 tensor。元组（只能作为关键字参数）的长度"
"必须等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.signbit.signbit:10 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "为 True 的值表示在该位置计算 ufunc，为 False 的值表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.signbit.signbit of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.signbit.signbit:15 of
msgid "**result** -- Output tensor, or reference to `out` if that was supplied."
msgstr "**result** -- 输出 tensor，如果提供了 `out` 则返回其引用。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.signbit.signbit of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

